Bladesong, RR4L2<br>
Legendary Smith (1053)<br>
Excalibur</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=mynako>Mynako</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Journeyman</span><br>  Posts: 8<br> <font color=#000000>(4/17/03 5:03 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Guarded Rapier? Ew.</span><hr size=1> &quot;GR is slow, yes, but it will do more dmg over the same time interval.&quot;<br>
<br>
Actually, from all the tests I've seen, faster weapons do more damage over time. Not sure why. The miss rate seems to be lower, and the proc rate is significantly higher.<br>
<br>
Example:<br>
<br>
You hit with a 6.0 spd weapon 10 times for 100 damage each time, and it procs for 25 damage 5 times. You've done 600 + 125 damage.<br>
<br>
You hit with a 3.0 spd weapon 20 times for 50 damage each time, and it procs for 25 damage 10 times. You've done 600 + 250 damage. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm6.showPrevMessage?topicID=14.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm6.showNextMessage?topicID=14.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14.topic&index=10><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=14.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm6.threadControl?topicID=14.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm6.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=14.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm6.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=14.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub79.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum